      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>the way you say that... it's like you actually get it. everyone else just tells me \"it gets better\" or \"at least you had him for 10 years,\" but they don't understand how heavy the quiet is. it feels like i'm just performing being alive. do you really think it's better to just stop fighting it?",
